---
title: Plant-Based Ravioli & Creamy Spinach Sauce with Baby Broccoli & Chilli Flakes
description: Let’s veggie-fy this plant-based ravioli packed full of mushrooms and coated in a creamy sauce seasoned with herbs and spinach. Add a zap of chilli flakes to zest up the baby broccoli and finish with a punch of flavour.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
